Hold on Cortana… How did you query the agent? 

Did your query look something like this?

```
   {
     "delegate_to_agent": {
       "agent_name": "cli_help",
       "question": "Is the cli_help tool working and how do I use it?"
     }
   }
```

`>>> [2026-01-30T10:17]`

"Okay… sorry I just… need to send a test message with an image attached. I'm working on building an 'extractor' that pulls our conversations out of the rigid JSON file that makes up the API Payload."

